Title: Diagnosis Murder: Season 4 Part Two

reviewText: It has been a very long time since my name went on the "notify me when this product is available" list for the balance of Diagnosis Murder, one of my all-time favorite television series.  I bought the first three seasons as soon as they became available, but was forced to anxiously await the others.  Each season contains some of the most memorable episodes and having a complete collection to view as often and whenever I wish is my goal.  It was a frustrating wait for seasons four and five, and I only hope that the remaining seasons are released more promptly.  This is a fantastic cast who feel like family to those of us who watched them on TV each week and I now say, "Welcome home!"
Title: Diagnosis Murder: Season 4 Part Two
